<para style="p">For the chief musician; with wind instruments. A psalm of David.</para>

<para style="b" />

<para style="q1">

<verse number="1" style="v" />Listen to my call to you, Yahweh;</para>

<para style="q1">think about my groanings.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="2" style="v" />Listen to the sound of my call, my King and my God,</para>

<para style="q1">for it is to you that I pray.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="3" style="v" />Yahweh, in the morning you hear my cry;</para>

<para style="q1">in the morning I will bring my petition to you and wait expectantly.</para>
